Call to Order by Chair Logan Gatti

Roll Call 

Present: Almaria Baker, Brenda Erickson, Bob Erickson, Ricky Santiago, Jim Stammerman, Ruth Gao, Kathryn Hargraves, Carl Bensinger, Virginia Woodward, Dale Warren, Suzanne Kugler, Colin McDowell, Ted Michalik, Charlie Horton, Mike Ward, Betsy FosterLogan Gatti, Beverly Chester Burton, Kimberly Cecil-Jones, Roz Welch,Maria Sorolis, Nick Holmes, Laura Lydon, Charlie Todd, Mclean Shutt, Blake Gerstner, Simeon Pullem, Deric Senecal, Deb Wesslund

