Communication:
Beth created documents that are in the September folder that focus on How to Host Events for LDP and for adding on new precinct leaders or volunteers to your district.  Documents: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EJ1BbAAiLm3uBeaHKZk4zlyxBnxzp6Yl/view?usp=drive_link

