Platform:
Anyone can be on the committee but needs to sign up with Logan now.  OCT- create draft NOV- submit it to Exec Committee for review, then revise  DEC- submit

Volunteers:
8 new people (younger) came to the Volunteers meeting on Tues the 23rd. 
The Volunteers group is Deep Canvassing and will help LDs. They just need time, date, and location from the LD chairs. They will train the precinct leaders/district volunteers on canvassing and go out in pairs. The next general meeting is on the calendar.

Open issues

	•	Robin Foxx (at large) updated on NOIR- They had an event at Algonquin Park last Saturday and had a good response- got information from citizens on issues that matter to them in their community - Did phone banking with black women- Will be going to Central High School to register voters there. Going to talk at Platinum Shears business to barbers and hair stylists. 
	•	Hallie Rice (at large)- Community Clean-ups (collabing with 50501) Parkhill area. Oct 11th- 5:30-7:30pm. Everyone invited to join. 
	•	Hispanic Heritage Month- Ricky Santiago, Cassie Blausey, Beth Thorpe, Jessica Haggy getting something together for social media focused on “Why I am a Latino/Latina Democrat”
